snippet.title: Comic Con 2014 - Wonder Woman Costume Reveal with Gal Gadot! : Beyond The Trailer

localized.description:
Today our first look at Gal Gadot as Wonder Woman at Comic Con 2014 in full costume during the Warner Bros DC Hall H presentation!
http://bit.ly/subscribeBTT

Warner Bros and DC give us our first look at Gal Gadot as Wonder Woman for Batman v Superman Dawn of Justice in 2016!  In full costume!  Do you think this Wonder Woman costume is as good as the one in the DC Comics, better or worse?  Does Gal Gadot look like Wonder Woman to you in this costume?  What do you think of the tiara, lasso, sword and armor?  And how does this make you feel about Batman v Superman in 2016?  And be sure to tune into Beyond The Trailer for today’s top news from Comic Con 2014 in San Diego, including panels, announcements, reveals, posters and more!

Interact with host & creator Grace Randolph!
